ent%20overhaul%20could%20affect%20Americans%20seeking%20advanced%20degrees%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223368%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22President%20Donald%20Trump%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68dfd3a7cc993f9955cf75de%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222246%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPresident%20Donald%20Trump's%20student-loan%20repayment%20overhaul%20would%20place%20new%20borrowing%20caps%20on%20graduate%20and%20professional%20degree%20programs.%3Cp%3EAlex%20Wong%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20Education%20Department%20concluded%20its%20first%20week%20of%20negotiations%20on%20overhauling%20student-loan%20repayment.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EOne%20of%20the%20changes%20is%20new%20caps%20on%20borrowing%20for%20graduate%20and%20professional%20students.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ENegotiators%20raised%20concerns%20that%20a%20narrow%20definition%20for%20a%20professional%20program%20could%20shut%20students%20out%20of%20aid.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20could%20soon%20be%20harder%20to%20finance%20your%20professional%20or%20graduate%20degree%20program.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPresident%20Donald%20Trump's%20Department%20of%20Education%20concluded%20its%20first%20week%20of%20negotiations%20on%20its%20plan%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmajor-student-loan-debt-repayment-changes-trump-kicks-off-negotiations-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eoverhaul%20student-loan%20repayment%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Friday.%20The%20discussions%20centered%20on%20Trump's%20changes%20to%20student%20loans%2C%20which%20he%20signed%20into%20law%20in%20his%20%26quot%3Bbig%20beautiful%26quot%3B%20spending%20bill.%20These%20included%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-borrowers-major-repayment-overhaul-big-beautiful-bill-trump-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecreating%20new%20income-driven%20repayment%20plans%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20placing%20new%20caps%20on%20borrowing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20latter%20topic%20was%20a%20central%20focus%20of%20negotiations.%20The%20department%20proposed%20eliminating%20the%20Grad%20PLUS%20loan%20program%2C%20which%20allows%20graduate%20and%20professional%20students%20to%20borrow%20up%20to%20the%20full%20cost%20of%20attendance.%20In%20addition%2C%20the%20department%20wants%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-spending-bill-student-loans-cap-graduate-school-doctor-lawyer-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eimplement%20new%20borrowing%20caps%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20for%20graduate%20students%2C%20%2420%2C500%20a%20year%20and%20%24100%2C000%20over%20a%20lifetime%3B%20and%20for%20professional%20students%2C%20%2450%2C000%20a%20year%20and%20%24200%2C000%20over%20a%20lifetime.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20the%20caps%2C%20the%20department%20wrote%20in%20its%20draft%20text%20that%20the%20higher%20cap%20for%20professional%20degrees%20will%20be%20limited%20to%2010%20programs%3A%20pharmacy%2C%20dentistry%2C%20veterinary%20medicine%2C%20chiropractic%2C%20law%2C%20medicine%2C%20optometry%2C%20osteopathic%20medicine%2C%20podiatry%2C%20and%20theology.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EClare%20McCann%2C%20managing%20director%20of%20policy%20and%20operations%20at%20American%20University's%20Postsecondary%20Education%20and%20Economic%20Research%20Center%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20list%20of%20programs%20is%20based%20on%20a%20current%2C%20%26quot%3Bnon-exhaustive%2C%26quot%3B%20definition%20of%20a%20professional%20degree.%20Some%20negotiators%20expressed%20concerns%20with%20limiting%20programs%20that%20qualify%20for%20the%20higher%20borrowing%20cap%2C%20and%20while%20the%20department%20indicated%20that%20it%20would%20be%20open%20to%20discussing%20changes%20to%20the%20list%2C%20it%20likely%20won't%20happen%20during%20the%20current%20round%20of%20negotiations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20this%20point%2C%20we%20would%20like%20to%20keep%20the%20language%20where%20it%20is%2C%26quot%3B%20Tamy%20Abernathy%2C%20the%20director%20of%20policy%20coordination%20at%20the%20department%2C%20said%20during%20the%20Tuesday%20session.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20an%20exhaustive%20list%2C%20but%20it%20is%20fixed%20at%20this%20point%20in%20time%2C%20with%20the%20caveat%20that%20if%20it%20needs%20to%20be%20negotiated%20at%20a%20future%20date%2C%20it%20would%20be.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20department%20will%20hold%20additional%20negotiation%20sessions%20in%20November%20to%20continue%20discussing%20the%20borrowing%20changes%20before%20moving%20toward%20the%20final%20implementation%20of%20the%20changes%20in%20July%202026.%20The%20department%20said%20the%20motivation%20behind%20these%20changes%20is%20to%20curb%20excessive%20student%20borrowing%2C%20but%20education%20experts%20told%20Business%20Insider%20it%20could%20limit%20financing%20options%20for%20borrowers%20seeking%20advanced%20degrees%2C%20either%20leading%20them%20to%20forgo%20enrollment%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-repayment-changes-student-loan-borrowers-private-lending-navient-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eturn%20to%20private%20lending%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20some%20pretty%20significant%20reductions%20in%20federal%20borrowing%20that%20are%20going%20to%20leave%20a%20lot%20of%20borrowers%20needing%20to%20find%20other%20ways%20to%20fill%20their%20financing%20gaps%20if%20they%20want%20to%20be%20able%20to%20continue%20to%20enroll%2C%26quot%3B%20McCann%20said.%20%26quot%3BFor%20some%20people%2C%20they%20may%20find%20it's%20not%20possible%20or%20not%20worth%20it%20to%20take%20on%20that%20additional%20private%20debt%2C%20assuming%20that%20colleges%20don't%20simply%20lower%20their%20tuition.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Caside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDo%20you%20have%20thoughts%20to%20share%20on%20the%20proposed%20student-loan%20changes%3F%20Reach%20out%20to%20this%20reporter%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3A%2520asheffey%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Easheffey%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Faside%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c053a7ab-4c94-475d-ac13-290daf3a53de%5C%22%3EGraduate%20and%20professional%20degree%20changes%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20negotiators%20agreed%20with%20the%20intent%20of%20curbing%20excessive%20borrowing%2C%20some%20were%20worried%20that%20the%20limits%20on%20professional%20degree%20programs%20would%20be%20detrimental%20to%20those%20in%20mental%20health%20careers%20who%20would%20not%20fit%20into%20the%20department's%20eligibility%20for%20the%20higher%20professional%20borrowing%20cap.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20couple%20thousand%20schools%20that%20offer%20clinical%20psychology%20that%20will%20be%20devastated%20to%20hear%20this%2C%20and%20this%20is%20the%20kind%20of%20program%20that%20requires%20about%20five%20years%20of%20study.%20And%20because%20of%20the%20limits%20involved%2C%20it's%20virtually%20impossible%20to%20drop%20below%20to%20the%20graduate%20level%20of%20funding%20on%20mental%20health%20programs%20like%20a%20doctoral%20in%20clinical%20psychology%2C%26quot%3B%20Andy%20Vaughn%2C%20president%20of%20Alliant%20International%20University%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBennett%20Boggs%2C%20commissioner%20of%20the%20Missouri%20Department%20of%20Higher%20Education%20%26amp%3B%20Workforce%20Development%2C%20added%20that%20the%20list%20is%20missing%20programs%20like%20engineering%2C%20business%2C%20commerce%2C%20and%20education.%20%26quot%3BThere%20are%20some%20professions%20here%20that%20are%20crucial%20to%20our%20state%20economic%20development%20and%20workforce%20development%2C%20and%20this%20list%20doesn't%20have%20it%2C%20so%20I'm%20concerned%20this%20is%20going%20to%20really%20cripple%20certain%20aspects%20of%20what%20we're%20trying%20to%20get%20done%20here%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20response%20to%20negotiators'%20concerns%2C%20the%20department%20proposed%20a%20new%20%26quot%3Binterim%20definition%26quot%3B%20for%20professional%20students.%20This%20definition%20allows%20a%20student%20to%20be%20considered%20a%20professional%20student%20if%20they%20were%20enrolled%20in%20a%20program%20that%20awards%20a%20professional%20degree%20before%20July%201%2C%202027.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20department's%20timeline%20for%20implementing%20these%20new%20borrowing%20caps%20could%20also%20complicate%20things.%20McCann%20said%20that%20colleges%20won't%20know%20the%20final%20rules%20until%20close%20to%20the%20start%20of%20the%20financial%20aid%20awards%20year%2C%20and%20prospective%20students%20might%20start%20applying%20for%20their%20programs%20without%20knowing%20how%20their%20aid%20will%20be%20structured.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENicholas%20Kent%2C%20the%20undersecretary%20of%20education%2C%20said%20during%20remarks%20at%20the%20start%20of%20negotiations%20that%20the%20department%20stands%20by%20the%20changes%20and%20its%20goal%20to%20simplify%20student-loan%20repayment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20moment%20to%20rise%20out%20of%20a%20system%20that%20has%20failed%20too%20many%20students%20for%20far%20too%20long%2C%26quot%3B%20Kent%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20call%20to%20reset%20and%20strengthen%20the%20federal%20government's%20role%20in%20helping%20students%20finance%20their%20higher%20education%20and%20borrowers%20repay%20their%20loans%20with%20a%20system%20that%20is%20simpler%2C%20more%20accountable%2C%20and%20better%20aligned%20with%20the%20needs%20of%20today's%20learners%2C%20workers%2C%20and%20families.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrumps-student-loan-debt-repayment-overhaul-borrowing-caps-professional-degrees-2025-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1759662661000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68dfd3af5dbc4fd10daa1d5e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.busines