0platform%20Webull%20also%20says%20it's%20seen%20the%20number%20of%20users%20on%20its%20learning%20platform%20grow%2037%25%20over%20the%20last%20three%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETraderDaddy's%20Alhanti%2C%20who%20worked%20as%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finvesting%2Fwhat-does-a-financial-advisor-do%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efinancial%20advisor%3C%2Fa%3E%20before%20becoming%20a%20trading%20instructor%2C%20said%20he%20witnessed%20firsthand%20the%20surge%20in%20interest%20in%20trading%20courses%20and%20groups%2C%20such%20as%20the%20one%20he%20runs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20a%20lot%20of%20it%20is%20the%20same%20story%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20of%20the%20wave%20of%20newcomers%20in%20recent%20years.%20%26quot%3B'I%20was%20watching%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpopular-stock-market-influencers-daytrading-wallstreetbets-reddit-retail-investing-strategy-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etrading%20on%20social%20media%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20saw%20people%20doing%20it%2C%20and%20I%20tried%20to%20teach%20myself%20on%20YouTube.%20I%20couldn't%20really%20find%20anyone%20else%20that%20was%20doing%20it%2C%20and%20I%20was%20just%20looking%20for%20someone%20to%20help%20me.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225333%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Traders%20in%20a%202-hour%20class%20led%20by%20Daniel%20Alhanti%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20Trader%20Daddy%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68dd66225dbc4fd10da9f7e1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223556%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAlhanti%2C%20who%20worked%20as%20a%20financial%20advisor%20before%20becoming%20a%20trading%20instructor%2C%20says%20he%20can%20identify%20a%20successful%20trader%20when%20he%20sees%20one.%3Cp%3EJutharat%20Pinyodoonyachet%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20class%20I%20attended%20took%20place%20in%20the%20evening%20and%20had%20about%2030%20people%20in