E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2290bce623-2aeb-4c45-bc84-1d03652b62b5%5C%22%3EAttendees%20were%20passionate%20about%20markets%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20seemed%20to%20be%20high%20enthusiasm%20for%20the%20market.%20In%20a%20side%20discussion%2C%20a%20few%20traders%20spoke%20heatedly%20about%20option%20contracts%20for%20Palantir%20and%20whether%20a%20particular%20trade%20had%20been%20profitable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20they%20just%20want%20to%20make%20money%20more%20than%20anything%2C%26quot%3B%20Gerardo%20Arevalo%2C%20a%20trader%20at%20the%20event%2C%20told%20me%2C%20speaking%20about%20the%20work%20ethic%20of%20the%20group.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlhanti%20says%20he%20can%20tell%20when%20a%20trader%20will%20be%20successful.%20%26quot%3BYou%20can%20see%20it%20in%20their%20eyes%20when%20they%20focus%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20me%20after%20the%20class.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBecoming%20a%20successful%20trader%20is%20notoriously%20hard.%20A%202020%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpapers.ssrn.com%2Fsol3%2Fpapers.cfm%3Fabstract_id%3D3423101%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estudy%3C%2Fa%3E%20found%20that%2097%25%20of%20investors%20who%20traded%20for%20more%20than%20300%20days%20lost%20money%2C%20and%20less%20than%201%25%20earned%20%2454%20or%20more%20a%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e39b6405-49c4-469f-acf1-4f56025e76f0%5C%22%3ETechnical%20analysis%20and%20independent%20thinking%20were%20emphasized%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20two%20hours%2C%20Alhanti%20walked%20the%20group%20through%20candlestick%20charts%20and%20technical%20analysis%20for%20trades%20he%20said%20his%20students%20were%20most%20interested%20in%2C%20which%20included%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fstocks%2Faapl-stock%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EApple%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fstocks%2Ftsla-stock%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ETesla%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fstocks%2Fintc-stock%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EIntel%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20the%20broader%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Findex%2Fs%26amp%3Bp_500%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ES%26amp%3BP%20500%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20goal%20was%20to%20identify%20a%20price%20breakout%E2%80%94such%20as%20when%20a%20stock%20suddenly%20trades%20above%20its%20200-day%20moving%20average%E2%80%94and%20of%20course%2C%20buy%20at%20the%20right%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlhanti%20said%20he%20wanted%20to%20see%20traders%20become%20confident%20and%20skilled%20enough%20to%20make%20their%20own%20decisions%20when%20trading%2C%20as%20opposed%20to%20relying%20on%20him%20to%20tell%20them%20when%20to%20buy%20and%20sell.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESometimes%2C%20when%20traders%20in%20the%20group%20make%20a%20profit%2C%20they%20text%20Alhanti%20in%20a%20panic%2C%20asking%20him%20what%20to%20do%20next%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDo%20not%20just%20blindly%20follow%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20to%20the%20class.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224dbfcfbc-4afe-4f40-8a74-b01a29aed2b2%5C%22%3EMany%20desire%20to%20quit%20their%20jobs%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EA%20strong%20desire%20for%20financial%20freedom%20was%20a%20common%20sentiment%20among%20the%20aspiring%20traders.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJoshua%20Villas%2C%20a%2023-year-old%20trader%20who%20sat%20in%20the%20back%2C%20told%20me%20he'd%20spent%20more%20than%20%24900%20on%20trading%20courses.%20He%20said%20he%20became%20interested%20in%20trading%20after%20a%20conversation%20with%20a%20friend%20not%20long%20after%20graduating%20from%20high%20school.%20The%20gist%20of%20the%20conversation%20was%20that%20day-trading%20was%20a%20ticket%20to%20financial%20freedom.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJust%20hearing%20that%20and%20knowing%20that%20someone%20told%20you%20and%20actually%20seeing%20it's%20real%20%E2%80%94%20You%20kind%20of%20just%20keep%20going%20and%20trying%2C%26quot%3B%20Villas%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVillas%2C%20who%20was%20recently%20laid%20off%20from%20his%20job%20as%20a%20stylist%2C%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BI'd%20say%20the%20end%20goal%20is%20just%20not%20to%20have%20to%20worry%20about%20survival.%20I%20would%20be%20happy%20if%20I%20was%20just%20able%20to%20make%20enough%20to%20keep%20living.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222667%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Daniel%20Alhanti%20speaking%20to%20traders%20in%20a%20coworking%20space%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68dd68d55dbc4fd10da9f844%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAlhanti%20says%20he%20frequently%20comes%20across%20aspiring%20traders%20who%20say%20they%20feel%20lost%20or%20stuck%20in%20their%20careers.%3Cp%3EJutharat%20Pinyodoonyachet%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20a%20common%20story%20among%20many%20traders%20Alhanti%20works%20with.%20In%20recent%20years%2C%20he%20says%20he's%20met%20more%20younger%20people%20who%20are%20aspiring%20traders%2C%20people%20who%20are%20unsure%20of%20how%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmillennial-gen-z-entry-level-job-market-shift-economy-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Estart%20their%20careers%3C%2Fa%3E%20but%20want%20income%20and%20are%20seeking%20mentorship.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20don't%20really%20know%20what%20type%20of%20career%20they%20want%2C%20or%20where%20to%20go%2C%20or%20what%20to%20do%2C%20but%20they%20know%20that%20they%20want%20to%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foveremployed-lessons-pros-cons-secretly-working-multiple-remote-jobs-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emultiple%20incomes%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20their%20life%2C%20trading%20being%20one%20of%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20Alhanti%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYacoub%20Rahman%2C%20a%2021-year-old%20college%20student%20who%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffuture-side-hustle-more-popular-traditional-jobs-extinct-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etrades%20on%20the%20side%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20said%20his%20goal%20is%20also%20to%20one%20day%20become%20a%20full-time%20trader.%20That%20endpoint%20is%20appealing%2C%20largely%20because%20trading%20%26quot%3Bfull-time%26quot%3B%20isn't%20anything%20like%20working%20a%20full-time%20job%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20think%20it%20would%20take%20a%20long%20time.%20Two%20or%20three%20hours%2C%20I%20guess%20that's%20enough%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20predicted%20about%20the%20amount%20of%20work%20required%20each%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERahman%20said%20he%20spent%20around%20three%20hours%20a%20day%20studying%20the%20market%20after%20completing%20his%20schoolwork.%20He%20added%20that%20he%20aspired%20to%20one%20day%20have%20plenty%20of%20free%20time%20to%20travel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EArevalo%2C%20a%2050-year-old%20trader%20and%20computer%20programmer%2C%20said%20he%20had%20effectively%20entered%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmillennial-retire-early-stop-working-investing-stocks-day-trading-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eearly%20retirement%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20was%20looking%20to%20trade%20for%20a%20living.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20trading%2C%20Arevalo%20said%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fworkers-job-hugging-hopping-labor-market-growth-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ejob-hopped%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20as%20he%20was%20past%20his%20prime%20as%20a%20coder%20and%20felt%20expendable%20to%20companies%20he%20worked%20for.%20He%20now%20spends%20six%20to%20eight%20hours%20a%20day%20trading.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlhanti%20says%20he%20feels%20bad%20for%20many%20of%20the%20traders%20who%20come%20to%20him%20feeling%20lost%20in%20their%20careers%2C%20particularly%20younger%20people.%20He%20himself%20was%20caught%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjob-search-advice-great-recession-graduates-gen-z-hiring-2025-7%5C%22