20of%20the%20fanciest%2C%20along%20with%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchase-sapphire-reserve-credit-card-795-annual-fee-perks-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChase%20Sapphire%20Reserve%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Sure%2C%20the%20black%20cards%20are%20ultra-elite%2C%20but%20they%20also%20come%20with%20an%20ultra-elite%20annual%20fee%20of%20thousands%20of%20dollars.%20The%20more%20accessible%20Amex%20and%20Chase%20cards%20have%20a%20champagne%20taste%20on%20a%20beer%20budget%20feel%20to%20them%2C%20explains%20Ted%20Rossman%2C%20a%20senior%20credit%20cards%20industry%20analyst%20at%20Bankrate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20far%20as%20the%20mass%20market%2C%20these%20are%20at%20the%20high%20end%2C%26quot%3B%20Rossman%20says.%20%26quot%3BI'm%20questioning%20if%20this%20is%20even%20mass%20market%20anymore.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHard%20same.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20increasingly%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcostco-new-hours-fees-changing-prices-tiers-customer-caste-system-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estratified%20consumer%20landscape%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20fancy%20rewards%20cards%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbuy-it-for-life-status-symbols-rolex-le-creuset-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estatus%20symbols%3C%2Fa%3E.%20They%20provide%20access%20to%20special%20deals%20and%20perks.%20They're%20a%20way%20to%20separate%20yourself%20from%20the%20rest.%20They%20can%20also%20feel%20like%20a%20trap%2C%20especially%20for%20those%20of%20us%20who%20aren't%20particularly%20inclined%20to%20do%20a%20bunch%20of%20points-counting.%20Is%20access%20to%20an%20increasingly%20overcrowded%20airport%20lounge%20worth%201%25%20of%20the%20median%20income%20in%20America%3F%20While%20I've%20enjoyed%20the%20Amex%20experience%2C%20I%20also%20have%20my%20doubts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EAmex%20used%20to%20be%20the%20type%20of%20card%20that%20was%20mainly%20reserved%20for%20wealthier%2C%20older%20people%2C%20and%20if%20you%20couldn't%20afford%20it%2C%20you%20could%20always%20lie%20and%20say%20you%20didn't%20want%20an%20Amex%20card%20because%20many%20merchants%20didn't%20take%20them.%20But%20that's%20changed.%20Amex%20is%20accepted%20pretty%20much%20everywhere%2C%20and%20young%20people%20are%20flocking%20to%20it%3A%20Millennials%20and%20Gen%20Z%20make%20up%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-american-express-card-holders-better-fico-scores-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E60%25%20of%20its%20new%20customers%3C%2Fa%3E%20worldwide.%20The%20company%20is%20betting%20that%20its%20enthusiastic%20customer%20base%2C%20young%20and%20old%2C%20won't%20be%20scared%20off%20by%20the%2029%25%20increase%20in%20its%20annual%20fee.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmex%20is%20selling%20its%20%24200%20bump%20to%20consumers%20by%20adding%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famerican-express-amex-platinum-card-refresh-annual-fee-benefits-changes-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enew%20benefits%3C%2Fa%3E%20it%20says%20could%20be%20worth%20up%20to%20%243%2C500.%20It's%20added%20new%20annual%20credits%20for%20%24400%20that%20can%20be%20spent%20with%20restaurant%20booking%20app%20Resy%20(which%20it%20owns)%2C%20%24300%20with%20Lululemon%2C%20and%20%24120%20with%20Uber%20One%2C%20among%20others%2C%20and%20has%20upped%20a%20credit%20that%20can%20be%20put%20toward%20digital%20entertainment%20services%20such%20as%20YouTubeTV%20and%20Paramount%2B%20to%20%24300%20a%20year.%20Amex%20has%20also%20increased%20the%20hotel%20credits%20that%20platinum%20members%20can%20access%2C%20and%20it's%20retaining%20existing%20benefits%2C%20such%20as%20credits%20for%20airline%20fees%2C%20Walmart%2B%2C%20Saks%2C%20and%20Equinox.%20It's%20part%20of%20Amex%20Platinum's%20ongoing%20shift%20from%20travel%20card%20to%20lifestyle%20card.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnytime%20these%20changes%20come%2C%20the%20justification%20is%20all%20the%20slew%20of%20added%20benefits%20that%20they%20are%20marketing.%20And%20to%20be%20clear%2C%20those%20benefits%20can%20easily%20outweigh%20the%20increased%20annual%20fee%20%E2%80%94%20the%20primary%20word%20there%20being%20%3Cem%3Ecan%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Nick%20Ewen%2C%20senior%20editorial%20director%20at%20The%20Points%20Guy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EReading%20through%20those%20benefits%2C%20my%20first%20instinct%20is%20that%20I%20should%20%3Cem%3Eabsolutely%20%3C%2Fem%3Ekeep%20the%20card.%20But%20I've%20spent%20the%20past%20week%20or%20so%20looking%20through%20what%20I'm%20actually%20using%20and%20%E2%80%A6%20man%2C%20I%20wish%20I%20were%20more%20organized.%20I've%20gotten%20the%20Walmart%2B%20credit%20every%20month%2C%20but%20I've%20never%20ordered%20a%20single%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Famazon-prime-vs-walmart-plus%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ething%20from%20Walmart%2B%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Besides%20the%20welcome%20bonus%2C%20I%20haven't%20even%20managed%20to%20rack%20up%2010%2C000%20more%20points.%20I'd%20forgotten%20to%20switch%20a%20lot%20of%20my%20qualifying%20streaming%20services%20to%20my%20Platinum%20card%2C%20so%20I'm%20missing%20out%20on%20that%20money.%20I%20ordered%20the%20cheapest%20item%20I%20actually%20wanted%20from%20Saks%20to%20get%20the%20%2450%20back%2C%20but%20even%20after%20the%20discount%2C%20I%20ended%20up%20spending%20%248%2C%20thanks%20mostly%20to%20the%20Platinum%20card%20pressure.%20As%20much%20as%20the%20airport%20lounge%20is%20a%20cute%20little%20treat%2C%20I%20miss%20the%20camaraderie%20of%20the%20regular%20airport%20bar.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20I've%20signed%20up%20for%20in%20getting%20the%20Amex%20Platinum%20card%20is%20essentially%20a%20%26quot%3Bhigh-end%20coupon%20book%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Michael%20Miller%2C%20an%20analyst%20at%20Morningstar%20Research%2C%20and%20it's%20up%20to%20me%20to%20figure%20out%20how%20to%20use%20those%20coupons.%20%26quot%3BYou%20kind%20of%20have%20to%20reshape%20your%20spending%20patterns%20around%20Amex's%20merchant%20partners%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20Amex%20raises%20its%20annual%20fee%20too%20high%2C%20it%20risks%20losing%20some%20customers%2C%20but%20thus%20far%2C%20people%20have%20generally%20been%20willing%20to%20pony%20up.%20The%20company%20says%20it%20has%20a%2098%25%20retention%20rate%20on%20the%20Platinum%20card.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI've%20often%20been%20asked%2C%20what%20is%20the%20ceiling%3F%20Where%20can%20these%20annual%20fees%20go%3F%20And%20we%2C%20transparently%2C%20likely%20haven't%20seen%20that%20ceiling%2C%26quot%3B%20Ewen%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCustomers%20understand%20what%20they%20are%20getting%20and%20are%20willing%20to%20pay%20for%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Anthony%20Cirri%2C%20Amex's%20executive%20vice%20president%20of%20US%20consumer%20cards%2C%20in%20an%20emailed%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20some%20consumers%20drop%20off%2C%20from%20a%20corporate%20perspective%2C%20it%20may%20not%20be%20the%20worst%20thing%20in%20the%20world.%20Amex's%20pitch%20to%20merchants%20is%20that%20offering%20discounts%20and%20credits%20will%20steer%20an%20affluent%20Amex%20Platinum%20customer%20base%20in%20their%20direction.%20It's%20not%20clear%20exactly%20how%20much%20each%20merchant%20kicks%20in%20to%20be%20part%20of%20the%20deal%2C%20but%20according%20to%20Amex%2C%20its%20partners%20bear%20more%20than%20a%20quarter%20of%20the%20overall%20cost%20of%20rewards.%20Discussing%20American%20Express's%20partnership%20with%20Saks%20in%20a%202018%20earnings%20call%2C%20CEO%20Stephen%20Squeri%20said%20that%20Amex's%20cost%20was%20zero.%20The%20higher%20the%20fee%20on%20the%20Platinum%20card%2C%20the%20more%20self-selection%20of%20high-income%20consumers%20that%20merchants%20want%20to%20get%20in%20the%20door.%20And%20people%20who%20can't%20stomach%20the%20cost%20can%20always%20downgrade%20to%20another%20Amex%20card%20while%20staying%20in%20the%20overall%20ecosystem.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSome%20of%20the%20philosophy%20here%20is%20to%20kind%20of%20double%20down%20on%20a%20truly%20luxury%20audience%2C%26quot%3B%20Rossman%20says.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20it%20almost%20seems%20to%20me%20that%20if%20they%20lose%20customers%20as%20a%20result%2C%20that's%20more%20of%20a%20feature%20than%20a%20bug.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmex%20isn't%20wrong%20about%20reshaping%20habits%20either.%20To%20try%20to%20take%20advantage%20of%20the%20Lululemon%20and%20Resy%20credits%20before%20they%20expire%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20quarter%20(they're%20split%20into%20four%20chunks%20across%20the%20year)%2C%20I%20made%20my%20very%20first%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flululemon-ceo-earnings-new-products-colors-trends-consumer-spend-behavior-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELululemon%20purchase%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20texted%20my%20boyfriend%20to%20make%20plans%20to%20go%20to%20a%20fancy%20restaurant%20over%20the%20weekend.%20Neither%20are%20purchases%20I%20would%20have%20made%20were%20it%20not%20for%20the%20platinum%20card%20deadline%20nipping%20at%20my%20heels.%20And%20yes%2C%20I%20spent%20more%20than%20intended%20at%20Lululemon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20people%20%3Cem%3Elove%20%3C%2Fem%3Etheir%20Amex%20Platinum%20cards.%20Madison%20Traughber%2C%2026%2C%20in%20Atlanta%2C%20is%20one%20of%20those%20Gen%20Zs%20who's%20obsessed%20with%20it.%20%26quot%3BYou%20can%20pry%20it%20from%20my%20cold%2C%20dead%2C%20hands%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%20She%20had%20anticipated%20the%20fee%20increase%20and%20thought%20it%20would%20be%20more.%20She%20rushed%20to%20Lululemon%20the%20day%20after%20the%20Amex%20partnership%20announcement%20and%20spied%20on%20others%20at%20the%20register%20to%20see%20if%20they%20were%20doing%20the%20same.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20almost%20a%20signal%20that%20you're%20in%20the%20know%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%20The%20most%20important%20perk%20to%20her%20is%20the%20airport%20lounge%20%E2%80%94%20she%20sometimes%20uses%20it%20to%20impress%20older%20coworkers.%20%26quot%3BYou%20get%20taken%20more%20seriously%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENot%20everyone's%20so%20eager%20to%20shell%20out%20more.%20Jim%20Hennessy%2C%2050%2C%20a%2015-year%20platinum-card%20member%20in%20Chicago%2C%20says%20he's%20still%20deciding%20whether%20to%20keep%20the%20card%20with%20the%20fee%20increase.%20The%20lounges%20are%20really%20crowded%20with%20chaotic%2020-somethings%20(my%20words%2C%20not%20his).%20He%20likes%20the%20Uber%20credit%20and%20some%20of%20the%20hotel%20rewards%2C%20but%20he%20has%20to%20do%20the%20math%20to%20see%20if%20they're%20still%20worth%20it.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20some%20of%20the%20exclusivity%20of%20the%20card's%20gone%20away%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20says%20it%20is%20investing%20heavily%20in%20lounges%2C%20including%20opening%20new%20ones%20in%20Amsterdam%2C%20Salt%20Lake%20City%2C%20and%20Newark.%20They%20are%20also%20launching%20a%20smaller%20%26quot%3Bsidecar%26quot%3B%20lounge%20concept%20in%202026.%20Ewen%2C%20from%20The%20Points%20Guy%2C%20pooh-poohs%20the%20lounge%20as%20part%20of%20the%20consumer%20equation%2C%20telling%20me%20it's%20a%20%26quot%3Bnice%20value-add%20above%20and%20beyond%20the%20monetary%20value%20I'm%20getting%20from%20my%20card.%26quot%3B%20Rossman%20reminds%20me%20that%20while%20travel-rewards%20cards%20%26quot%3Bget%20all%20the%20headlines%2C%26quot%3B%20more%20basic%20cash-back%20cards%20are%20actually%20Americans'%20favorite%20type%20of%20card.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETalking%20it%20through%20with%20people%2C%20I%20go%20back%20and%20forth%20on%20whether%20this%20nearly%20%24900%20card%20is%20worth%20it.%20One%20friend%20tells%20me%20he's%20an%20Amex%20%26quot%3BFREAK%26quot%3B%20and%20loves%20it%2C%20but%20if%20and%20when%20he%20stops%20traveling%20so%20much%20for%20work%2C%20he'll%20probably%20ax%20it%2C%20given%20the%20cost%2C%20and%20get%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fcredit-cards%2Fbest-cash-back-credit-cards%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecash-back%20card%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Another%20says%20the%20card%20is%20%26quot%3Bdope%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20because%20her%20family%20is%20military%2C%20she%20gets%20the%20fee%20waived.%20My%20modest%20Midwestern%20self%20%E2%80%94%20and%20my%20modest%20Midwestern%20mother's%20voice%20in%20the%20back%20of%20my%20head%20%E2%80%94%20tell%20me%20the%20price%20tag%20is%20ridiculous.%20A%20positive%3A%20Amex's%20app%20now%20helps%20you%20track%20how%20and%20whether%20you're%20using%20the%20benefits.%20A%20negative%3A%20You%20still%20have%20to%20enroll%20in%20a%20lot%20of%20the%20benefits%2C%20and%20they%20don't%20automatically%20kick%20in%20if%20you%20forget.%20A%20positive%3A%20I%20get%20a%20fair%20share%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fuber-fresh-days-grocery-discounts-delivery-wars-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUber%20discounts%3C%2Fa%3E%20thanks%20to%20Amex.%20A%20negative%3A%20I%20take%20more%20Ubers%20than%20I%20would%20otherwise.%20I'm%20lucky%20that%20I'm%20able%20to%20pay%20off%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fcredit-score%2Fhow-to-pay-off-debt-fast%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20my%20credit%20card%20bill%20%3C%2Fa%3Eat%20the%20end%20of%20every%20month%2C%20so%20I%20don't%20have%20to%20weigh%20the%20cost-benefit%20scenarios%20of%20interest%20versus%20perks.%20Plus%2C%20I%20push%20the%20fact%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fonlinelibrary.wiley.com%2Fdoi%2F10.1002%2Fpam.70020%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erewards%20cards%20are%20wealth%20transfers%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20the%20poor%20to%20the%20rich%20to%20the%20back%20of%20my%20mind.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20do%20think%20people%20need%20to%20really%20run%20the%20numbers%2C%20and%20there%20is%20a%20cost%20to%20complexity%2C%26quot%3B%20Rossman%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20fairly%20certain%20I%20have%20a%20little%20more%20time%20to%20decide%20whether%20I%20want%20to%20keep%20my%20Amex%20Platinum%20before%20the%20new%20higher%20fee%20takes%20effect.%20The%20fact%20that%20I%20still%20haven't%20looked%20up%20that%20deadline%20is%20also%20a%20sign%20that%20I'm%20probably%20better%20off%20canceling%2C%20but%20hope%20springs%20eternal.%20Maybe%20I'll%20become%20a%20spreadsheet%20gal.%20Maybe%20I%20can%20eat%20and%20drink%20my%20way%20through%20a%20few%20hundred%20dollars%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthings-to-never-do-airport-lounges-frequent-flyer%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eat%20the%20lounge%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Or%20maybe%20it's%20another%20lesson%20that%20the%20economy%20works%20best%20for%20the%20people%20who%20have%20the%20time%2C%20money%2C%20and%20patience%20to%20play%20it%20right.%20The%20platinum%20card%20isn't%20just%20about%20perks%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20about%20working%20the%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20do%20have%20to%20kind%20of%20go%20along%20with%20the%20game%20here%2C%26quot%3B%20Miller%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fauthor%2Femily-stewart%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EEmily%20Stewart%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20is%20a%20senior%20correspondent%20at%20Business%20Insider%2C%20writing%20about%20business%20and%20the%20economy.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famex-platinum-credit-card-new-annual-fee-regrets-2025-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1759653181000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68dff9225dbc4fd10daa24ba%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famex-platinum-credit-card-new-annual-fee-regrets-2025-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Amex%20Platinum%20Card%20is%20charging%20a%20new%20%24895%20annual%20fee.%20Despite%20the%20bene