%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20one%20of%20the%20main%20selling%20points%20for%20Joby%20and%20Archer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20companies%20are%20envisioning%20a%20ride-share-like%20service%20in%20dense%20urban%20regions%20%E2%80%94%20except%20they're%20relying%20on%20a%20zero-emissions%2C%20all-electric%20aircraft%20to%20transport%20passengers.%20Enter%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felectric-air-taxis-expected-to-fly-by-2025-infrastructure-challenges-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eflying%20taxis%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20achieve%20public%20acceptance%20of%20a%20fleet%20of%20small%20aircraft%20constantly%20hovering%20over%20people's%20heads%2C%20noise%20%E2%80%94%20along%20with%20safety%20%E2%80%94%20is%20among%20the%20top%20priorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20almost%20sounds%20like%20a%20whoosh%2C%26quot%3B%20Didier%20Papadopoulos%2C%20Joby's%20president%20of%20aircraft%20OEM%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20at%20the%20airshow.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20that%20allows%20it%20to%20blend%20in%20with%20the%20cities%20and%20the%20noise.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPublic%20opinion%20is%20only%20part%20of%20the%20hurdle.%20EVTOLs%20are%20a%20capital-intensive%20and%20highly%20regulated%20space.%20Companies%20undergo%20numerous%20tests%20and%2C%20in%20the%20US%2C%20must%20obtain%20several%20certifications%20to%20demonstrate%20airworthiness%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fflying-taxi-firm-archer-gets-faa-approval-for-commercial-operations-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EFederal%20Aviation%20Administration%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJoby%2C%20which%20was%20founded%20in%202009%2C%20has%20said%20that%20it%20aims%20to%20take%20its%20first%20passengers%20by%202026%20in%20Dubai.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EArcher%2C%20a%20seven-year-old%20company%2C%20announced%20in%20May%20that%20it%20would%20partner%20with%20the%20Los%20Angeles%202028%20Olympics%20to%20transport%20VIPs%20and%20fans%20between%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ekey%20venues%20for%20the%20games%2C%20including%20the%20Los%20Angeles%20Memorial%20Coliseum%2C%20and%20other%20visitor%20hubs%20such%20as%20the%20Los%20Angeles%20International%20Airport.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20Archer%20Aviation%20representative%20could%20not%20be%20reached%20for%20comment%20during%20the%20weekend.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EJoby%20conducted%20an%208-mile%20trip%20from%20the%20Marina%20Municipal%20Airport%20to%20the%20event%20in%20Salinas%2C%20south%20of%20the%20San%20Francisco%20Bay%20Area%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Joby%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68e1c3485dbc4fd10daa34e9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ELloyd%20Lee%2FBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjoby-flying-taxi-first-test-flight-us-airports-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EJoby's%20aircraft%3C%2Fa%3E%20features%20six%20tilting%20propellers%20that%20can%20rotate%20mid-flight%2C%20enabling%20the%20vehicle%20to%20seamlessly%20transition%20from%20vertical%20takeoff%20to%20forward%20flight.%20It%20also%20allows%20the%20aircraft%20to%20hover%20in%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%2010-minute%20showcase%2C%20Joby%20demonstrated%20a%20540-degree%20spin%20as%20it%20hovered%20in%20a%20single%20position.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EJoby's%20blades%20are%20designed%20to%20reduce%20the%20vehicle's%20noise%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Joby%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68e1ca011c1f80efbec4f29a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20blades%20of%20one%20of%20Joby's%20propellers.%3Cp%3ELloyd%20Lee%2FBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20combination%20of%20shorter%20blades%20and%20an%20electric%20propulsion%20system%20makes%20the%20Joby%20aircraft%20quieter%2C%20according%20to%20Papadopoulos.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBecause%20of%20the%20electric%20propulsion%2C%20you%20don't%20actually%20have%20to%20spin%20the%20motor%20as%20fast%20to%20get%20the%20torque%20that%20you%20need%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EJoby's%20cockpit%20has%20a%20flight%20control%20system%20that%20emulates%20an%20F-35%20fighter%20jet%2C%20Papadopoulos%20said%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Joby%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68e1c69c1c1f80efbec4f27c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20cockpit%20of%20Joby's%20aircraft.%3Cp%3ELloyd%20Lee%2FBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20cockpit%20of%20Joby's%20eVTOL%20was%20designed%20to%20be%20simple%2C%20Papadopoulos%20told%20BI.%20The%20simplicity%20is%20intended%20to%20make%20flying%20Joby%20feel%20intuitive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20advanced%20fly-by-wire%20flight%20control%20systems%20that%20you%20would%20see.%20It%20was%20really%20built%20on%20decades%20of%20research%20by%20NASA%2C%20Air%20Force%2C%20and%20so%20on%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20executive%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20see%20it%20when%20we%20bring%20in%20people%20who%20do%20not%20have%20aviation%20experience.%20It%20takes%20them%20about%2020%20minutes%20in%20the%20simulator%20of%20flying%2C%20and%20they%20are%20like%20totally%20natural.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EArcher%20Aviation%20conducted%20a%20more%20conventional%20takeoff%20from%20the%20Salinas%20Municipal%20Airport%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221821%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Archer%20Aviation%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68e1c0b7cc993f9955cf8ddd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221366%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EArcher%20Aviation's%20Midnight%20eVOTL.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20Archer%20Aviation%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%